<p>
<b><font style="font-size: 11pt">Do You Do Nails?</font></b><span style="font-family: Verdana"><b><span style="font-size: 11pt">
</span> </b></span><font style="font-size: 11pt">
<span style="FONT-WEIGHT: 400">by Tom Holloway</span></font></td>
<td width="27" height="26" align="right">
													
<a href="../../../hUS/hUS-index.asp">
<img border="0" src="../../00-000-globIncl/intNavImg/arrowBack.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a></td>
